Hello,

First of all - Thanks for all the work! This is a great component and I use it a lot!

I've been trying to use GoogleSatelliteMap lately but it seems it's not really working.

Is this a google issue? Or a licensing issue?
I'm using the latest GMap.NET version (just downloaded).

I'm based in Israel (but I've tried in other places with the same results)

Thanks
Nitay
